  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/6df5db1fbdff549fb3a40a86d143bbd6.avif?t=1745628078\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 8 players spawn in an enclosed arena where they must battle it out.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Taking damage results in increased knockback. Don't get hit out of the arena!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Obtaining rifts will grant players new weapons, spawn events, or give deadly curses.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For each round you survive,  you get money to help secure your victory!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.mp4?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/4510f7f146b6df2f4f51ece9b808a4e9.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/4510f7f146b6df2f4f51ece9b808a4e9.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/4510f7f146b6df2f4f51ece9b808a4e9.mp4?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/b70167b5ed7d906c608c1a0b7dfd4260.avif?t=1745628078\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 25+ arenas and more to come in future updates.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each arena has unique obstacles that make players adapt playstyle.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breakable Floors, Moveable Blocks, Swinging Maces, and more.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/83d23cb45cbcbd567c4c44614935b63b.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/83d23cb45cbcbd567c4c44614935b63b.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/83d23cb45cbcbd567c4c44614935b63b.mp4?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/1edfd32b86eef1ef631eda67be68ce57.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/1edfd32b86eef1ef631eda67be68ce57.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/1edfd32b86eef1ef631eda67be68ce57.mp4?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/3e5bbd0bd0563e2986e8f1d045a8a952.avif?t=1745628078\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons (Riftblade, Revolvers, Saws, etc.)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manipulations (Growth, Speed, Knockback, etc.)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Events (Lava, The Void, Blizzards, etc.)</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Curses (Explosion, Slowness, Marbles, etc.)</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
